	<body>
		<h3>CarClass定义 </h3>
        <pre class= code>
#define CarClass(name)      class name : public _##name
        </pre>
    <h3>使用说明 </h3>
        <p>1.在.car文件中声明一个CHello类，如下所示： </p>
        <pre class =code>
module www.elastos.com/car/HelloDemo.dll
{
    interface IHello{
        Hello();
    }
    class <b>CHello</b>{
        interface IHello;
    }
} 
        	
        </pre>        
        <p>2. 在.car文件编译之后会生成<b>CHello.h</b>的头文件，头文件中有如下定义: </p>
        <pre class =code>
#ifndef __CHELLO_H__
#define __CHELLO_H__
#include "_CHello.h"

<b>CarClass(CHello)     //在编译时被替换为：class CHello:public _CHello</b> 
{
public:
      CARAPI Hello();
private:
      // TODO: Add your private member variables here.
};
#endif // __CHELLO_H__
 	
        </pre>
	</body>
		
